拉左去，香港人已經好危險，隨時係大陸行街唔見左人。<br />\n<br />\n3 微博微信ig 喊打喊殺，粗口多到不堪入目，傳播仇恨，一定唔可以忽視。<br />\n<br />\n4 撐警集會一批批大陸人黎搞亂，又引入福建幫等，呢d都係用人民鎮壓人民的技倆。<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下，香港人呢個身分已經唔安全，隨時引黎殺機。"},{"pid":"71557e2d864a071bbc62e8d0d13a3910e5f7e65b","tid":1480326,"uid":151304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47295c89981067fffb3ccd1e608857cf18ee31a1","tid":1480326,"uid":166245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有班香港人寫咗封信多謝支持民主嘅韓國人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1480348/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1480348/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位幫手轉發，盡量令多D韓國人可以睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57190ff2157a5b30eaaafd0c516b2cfab20c2dd5","tid":1480326,"uid":151304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc8f6031dc295447e5a5028fc9792878f207bf8","tid":1480326,"uid":151304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b003ed182f992f7d8900adcba3f16d14f96c24ba","tid":1480326,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7722627b00e8063301a55c1e9f5cd021809501f7","tid":1480326,"uid":151304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p